OL,3,CStricken Dutch yacht prompts cross-
OL,4,Cchannel emergency response
OL,6,FThree people aboard a Dutch yacht have
OL,7,Fbeen forced to divert to Guernsey
OL,8,Fafter their boat suffered what the
OL,9,FCoastguard says was a "complete power
OL,10,Ffailure".
OL,12,FA distress call was issued from the
OL,13,F'Mad Science' vessel at around 4:40am
OL,14,Fon Wednesday 7 January, as it was
OL,15,Faround 11 nautical miles south of
OL,16,FGuernsey.
