OL,3,CStricken Dutch yacht prompts cross-
OL,4,Cchannel emergency response
OL,6,FIt managed to communicate with the
OL,7,FFrench Maritime Rescue Coordination
OL,8,FCentre (MRCC) that it had a major
OL,9,Fpower issue and was uncertain of its
OL,10,Fposition.
OL,12,FThe situation was then passed over to
OL,13,Fthe Guernsey Coastguard, which
OL,14,Fcontinued contact with the yacht that
OL,15,Fwas hoping to visit Brest in Brittany.
OL,17,FThe vessel reported being unable to
OL,18,Fsail after losing all electrical
OL,19,Fpower, but that its engine had been
OL,20,Frebooted and the crew wished to seek
OL,21,Fshelter in St Peter Port.
