OL,3,CStricken Dutch yacht prompts cross-
OL,4,Cchannel emergency response
OL,6,FHowever, radio contact was lost at
OL,7,Faround 5:40am and the St Peter Port
OL,8,Flifeboat was launched, following
OL,9,Fmultiple unsuccessful attempts by
OL,10,Fdifferent agencies and other nearby
OL,11,Fvessels to regain communication.
OL,13,FJust after 7am, the lifeboat found the
OL,14,Fstricken vessel around eight nautical
OL,15,Fmiles south of Guernsey and made
OL,16,Fdirect contact with the crew.
