OL,3,CStricken Dutch yacht prompts cross-
OL,4,Cchannel emergency response
OL,6,FThe yacht's navigation and
OL,7,Fcommunication equipment had failed,
OL,8,Fwhile the three crew were all
OL,9,Fsuffering from seasickness, so the
OL,10,Fboat was escorted into St Peter Port
OL,11,FHarbour.
OL,13,FGuernsey Coastguard's Duty Search and
OL,14,FRescue Coordinator, Simon Granger,
OL,15,Fsays: "This was an excellent example
OL,16,Fof multi-agency cooperation ensuring
OL,17,Fthe safety of those in distress."
